          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/48928025-serenade-for-nadia">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3503801946" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7520606989105994503">This was a love story from beginning to end. I loved the way Livaneli structured the book using Maya as the narrator. The book, with surprising frankness, talks about the many conflicts in Istanbul and in Turkey as a whole. I loved this book and I would read another by him.<br/>I will say I thought at times that the translation was a bit simple but it never hindered the story.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


