      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/17853832.Z_lf_Livaneli">About Zülfü Livaneli</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/17853832.Z_lf_Livaneli"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1522242943p3/17853832.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/17853832.Z_lf_Livaneli">Zülfü Livaneli
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
